description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 78, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 234, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, 3 for South, and 5 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40783-11352-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [234 Votes, Top 5% Score]
